# Google Apps Script Web App URL — satu URL untuk AUTH + Drive sync.
# Backend: scripts/apps-script-backend.js (menggantikan receiver lama).
#
# Setup:
# 1. Buka script.google.com → New Project
# 2. Paste SELURUH kode dari scripts/apps-script-backend.js
# 3. Deploy → Web App → Execute as: Me → Who has access: Anyone → Authorize
# 4. Copy URL hasil deploy ke sini (dan ke GitHub Secret untuk production)
VITE_APPS_SCRIPT_URL=https://script.google.com/macros/s/YOUR_SCRIPT_ID/exec
